{"tid":1859303,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鄭松泰：查詢（私立及直資）學校停課期間的學費及財政安排","createTime":"2020-02-03T07:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T07:59:05.000Z","uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae381ec69cecf02e367c3b08c578896ab6fb9aa7","tid":1859303,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T07:36:12.000Z","msg":"致  教育局：<br />\n <br />\n【查詢（私立及直資）學校停課期間的學費及財政安排】<br />\n <br />\n教育局日前宣佈全港中小學、幼稚園及特殊學校，最早於3月2日復課。本辦事處得知許多直資或私立學校都已經仿傚及跟隨，惟不少家長都關注學費的計算，因此本處致函  貴局查詢：<br />\n <br />\n（一）局方日前有否就收費安排諮詢各幼稚院、直資或私立學校；<br />\n <br />\n（二）局方會否考慮在財政上提供特別支援，使學校停課並免受學費的同時，保證其運作不會停頓？<br />\n<br />\n（三）不少幼兒教育中心都表示停課對其將來營運帶來負擔，局方有否措施協助他們渡過難關？<br />\n<br />\n（四）局方理應就停課決定，有責任協助私校家長與學校之間的溝通，特別是在學費、書簿雜費，及活動開支等問題上。局方會否主動跟進相關事宜？<br />\n <br />\n耑此函達，祈候示覆。<br />\n <br />\n鄭松泰立法會議員辦事處<br />\n<br />\n2020年2月3日<br />\n<br />\n註：信件相片後補<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCbA4mw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCbA4mw.jpg&h=4c209261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/396949433812753/posts/1422595684581451/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F396949433812753%2Fposts%2F1422595684581451%2F&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=6681f0f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/396949433812753/posts/1422595684581451/</a>"},{"pid":"a02793e7e8490cf51475f94bbac9210c761f6a41","tid":1859303,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"做實事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622d4ee3e381337ac464a5d652ddeac3d0e98b5c","tid":1859303,"uid":49018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T07:37:21.000Z","msg":"幾時幫手叫大學回水"},{"pid":"c2229162c898eab4fbbd4e4feda836d8e26dcd3e","tid":1859303,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"622d4ee3e381337ac464a5d652ddeac3d0e98b5c","tid":1859303,"uid":49018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T07:37:21.000Z","msg":"幾時幫手叫大學回水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T07:39:02.000Z","msg":"靠大學SU啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e1fa6736cd77242b17d021cef82a2247b78472","tid":1859303,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T07:59:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}